Let’s draw something fun and abstract. I use @blackwing pencils a lot in my abstract drawings. In this video I am showing Blackwing XIX and Blackwing 155 pencils. XIX one is perfect for draft drawings and sketching as it is a firm graphite. And Blackwing 155 is great for darker parts as it is more intense and it has a soft graphite core. 
.
I am a big fan of Blackwing pencils and If you are interested in buying and tryout Blackwing, you can use this link to order: https://blackwing602.com/gizem or use my code: GIZEMVURAL when you checkout.
.
I only recommend products I would use myself and all opinions expressed here are our own. This post may contain affiliate links that at no additional cost to you and I may earn a small commission.

Happy Holidays! / Happy New Year 🎄❤️✨

Before closing the year I wanted to say couple of things. It's been a hard year, not easy, while things happened, new stuff emerged in my life, also the world's situation, with war, evil AI and global warming really depressed me a lot. I pushed so hard to stay in the game, to create work for editorial and also draw new abstract pieces while exploring my inner world and make peace with some parts of myself that I never understood before. In the end I made a hard decision to stop working on editorial for a while I don't know how long yet. Because I love illustration but it is also hard, people who know me will understand what I am talking about. : ) Anyway, I will be focusing on me and my abstract work which I love. So thanks for being here, liking commenting or quietly observing. Wishing all a better new year. ❤️🎉
